title: Anachronox the Movie, Disc 1/2
description:
Anachronox the Movie, Disc 1/2

ISOs first released on Aug 2006 at <http://www.machinima.com/forums/viewtopic.php?t=6861>.  I am not affiliated with the parent poster in any way.

Also originally available from 2002/2003 in MPEG and/or AVI at Machinima.com (and also archive.org and FilePlanet).



These are close enough to the original torrents (anox_disc1.iso, anox_disc2.iso), only with updated tracker URLs.


from Machinima.com:
Anachronox: The Movie is a tour-de-force. One of the finest Machinima films produced to date, and probably the most accomplished Machinima feature to date. Hell, it managed to hold two over-worked jury members in a room for two and a half hours before the MFF 2002 - what more can we say?

from archive.org:
Based on the computer role playing game (RPG) of the same name, Anachronox: The Movie is a feature-length "Machinima" motion picture. In the 2002 Annual Machinima Awards, Anachronox was awarded: First place for best picture, first place for best writing, first place for best technical achievement, first place for best visual design, and first place for best editing.
